      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu Eesaws redseja / ka\nIhsääks Jehkabu bij swehtijis/un\nto uhs Mesopotamiju fuhtijs/ ka\ntain no turrenes bij Seewu nemt/\nun ka tas tain to swehtijoht / bij\npawehlejs / fazzidams : tew ne\nbuhs Seewu nemt no tahm Ka-\nnaniteru Meitahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ka Jehkabs fawam Teh-\nwam unfawai Mahtei bij paflau-\nfijis / un uhs Mesopotamiju\ngahjts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Eesaws arri redseja / ka\nIhsääks / winna Tehws / tahs\nKananiteru Meitus ne eeredseja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad gahje Eesaws pee Is-\nmaëta / un ehnte few par See-\nwu / pahr fawahin Seewahin\nMäätatu / Ismaëta Ahbrääina\nDehla Meitu/Nabajota Mahju.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad aisgahje Jehkabs no\nVersabas/nn gahje uhs Abranu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tam gaddijahs nahkt\nkaheä Weetä / tur palikke wiꞥſch\npar Nakti / jo ta Saute bij no-\ngahjufi/ un tas nehme weenu no\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tam fapnoja/ un rauf-\ngi/ Treppes bij zeltaä wirs Sem-\nmes / un winnu Wirs·Gals ais-\ntikke to Debbes/ un redsi/ tee Dee-\nwa Engeți uskahpe un nokahpe\npahr tahm.\n"
