    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un redsi / tas KUNGS\nstahweja pa wirsu / un fazzija\nEs esmu tas KUNGS / tawa\nTehwa Ahbrääina Deews / un\nIhsääka Deews / to Semmi /\nwirs ko tu gulli/dohschu es tew/\nun tawam Dsinmmnam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tawä Dsinmmnms buhe\nka Semmes Pihschli / un tu is-\nplattifees prett Wakkaru / un\nprett Rihteem / prett Seemeli/\nun prett Deenas-Widdu/un zaun\ntew un tawu SEHKLU tape\nwiffas Semmes Ziltis swehtitas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un reds/ es esmu ar tew/\nun pafargafchu tew wiffur / ku-\ntu staigasi / un pahrweddischu\nkans es darrischu/ ko es us tew\nefmu runnajis.\n"
    },
