      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu Jehkabs no fatwa\nMeega atmohdahs/fazzija tas:\nTeescham tas KUNGS irr schin-\nni Weeta/ un es to ne efmu sin-\nnajs.\n"
